0business%20leaders%20on%20how%20they're%20testing%20and%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cedars-sinai.org%2Fabout.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECedars-Sinai%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20nonprofit%20healthcare%20organization%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20It's%20comprised%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-health-system-location-tracking-technology-nurses-hospitals-safety-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clinics%2C%20and%20research%20facilities.%20Founded%20in%201902%2C%20Cedars-Sinai%20has%20more%20than%2040%20locations%2C%20employs%20over%204%2C500%20physicians%20and%20nurses%2C%20and%20serves%20more%20than%201%20million%20patients%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a5aba0e-3764-4aab-b571-852c2669ecab%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20analysis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECaroline%20Goldzweig%2C%20chief%20medical%20officer%20of%20Cedars-Sinai%20Medical%20Network%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20organization%20wanted%20to%20expand%20patients'%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-walgreens-amazon-primary-care-acquisition-strategy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprimary%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20convenient%20way.%20For%20instance%2C%20sometimes%20there%20are%20lengthy%20wait%20times%20for%20in-person%20doctor's%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Goldzweig%20said%20the%20organization%20was%20looking%20to%20reduce%20the%20administrative%20burden%20on%20physicians%2C%20including%20patient%20intake%20and%20data%20entry%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20focus%20on%20providing%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20challenges%2C%20the%20organization%20launched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsconnect.cedars-sinai.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECedars-Sinai%20Connect%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%20CS%20Connect%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-artificial-intelligence-customer-experience-business-applications-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E-powered%20virtual%20platform%20where%20patients%20can%20access%20healthcare%20support%2024%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-powerhouses-betting-on-healthcare-ai-amazon-nvidia-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20allows%20healthcare%20providers%20to%20better%20support%20their%20patients%20while%20improving%20the%20speed%20of%20care%20delivery.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20exciting%20thing%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20offer%20patients%20care%20in%20ways%20that%20meet%20their%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22914%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caroline%20Goldzweig%2C%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20of%20Cedars-Sinai%20Medical%20Network%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68769f08f748d8c055f5a832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Goldzweig%20is%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20of%20Cedars-Sinai%20Medical%20Network.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cedars-Sinai%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c338bd5e-a772-42d4-9bfd-1a5b5bb71f41%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKey%20staff%20and%20partners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20CS%20Connect%20was%20built%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-burnout-ai-assistant-help-paperwork-administrative-tasks-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EK%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20digital%20healthcare%20company%20providing%20AI-powered%20primary%20and%20urgent%20care%20services.%20Cedars-Sinai's%20information%20technology%20teams%20worked%20with%20K%20Health%20to%20sync%20patients'%20electronic%20health%20records%20into%20the%20platform%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECedars-Sinai's%20enterprise%20data%20intelligence%20and%20digital%20strategy%20teams%20were%20also%20involved%20in%20creating%20CS%20Connect.%20They%20continue%20to%20help%20manage%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d1d3540-8a19-423c-93f4-cfebeb920031%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20in%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20of%20the%20AI%20tool%20is%20to%20enable%20providers%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20counseling%20patients%20and%20making%20treatment%20decisions%2C%20rather%20than%20doing%20patient%20intake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20access%20the%20AI%20features%2C%20patients%20log%20into%20CS%20Connect%20via%20a%20mobile%20app%20or%20its%20website.%20Goldzweig%20said%20a%20chat%20feature%20then%20starts%20asking%20the%20user%20questions%20about%20their%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20algorithm%20compares%20the%20patient's%20responses%20to%20their%20existing%20medical%20records%20and%20the%20records%20of%20other%20patients%20in%20the%20system%20who%20had%20similar%20symptoms.%20It%20then%20asks%20more%20detailed%20questions%20about%20a%20patient's%20specific%20health%20problems.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20may%20prompt%20the%20patient%20to%20submit%20photos%20of%20their%20sore%20throat%20or%20rash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20said%20the%20chat%20function%20is%20similar%20to%20how%20a%20physician%20might%20identify%20a%20patient's%20ailment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20then%20summarizes%20the%20patient's%20information%20%E2%80%94%20a%20task%20that%20usually%20demands%20manual%20effort%20from%20physicians%20%E2%80%94%20and%20recommends%20a%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20collected%20by%20CS%20Connect%20is%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20efficiency%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldzweig%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20allows%20the%20physicians%20to%20review%20it%2C%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20and%20to%20validate%20things%20with%20the%20patient%20%E2%80%94%20ask%20a%20couple%20of%20clarifying%20questions%20and%20maybe%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20history.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhysicians%20can%20choose%20to%20disagree%20with%20the%20AI's%20recommendations.%20Goldzweig%20said%20either%20way%2C%20they're%20required%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20each%20patient's%20treatment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interface%20of%20CS%20Connect%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68769f6b3d5881a51c1d5fc1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22635%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECS%20Connect%20has%20a%20chatbot%20that%20can%20ask%20users%20about%20their%20symptoms%20and%20recommend%20a%20treatment.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Cedars-Sinai%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b85e560-b18c-4455-8875-3ee70d4a26dd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20it%20work%2C%20and%20how%20did%20leaders%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20told%20BI%20that%20about%2042%2C000%20individual%20patients%20have%20used%20CS%20Connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202025%2C%20Cedars-Sinai%20published%20a%20study%20in%20the%20journal%20Annals%20of%20Internal%20Medicine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acpjournals.org%2Fdoi%2F10.7326%2FANNALS-24-03283%3Futm_source%3Dmiragenews%26utm_medium%3Dmiragenews%26utm_campaign%3Dnews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomparing%20AI%20treatment%20recommendations%20in%20CS%20Connect%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20final%20recommendations%20from%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20reviewed%20461%20physician-managed%20visits%20with%20AI%20recommendations%20for%20respiratory%2C%20urinary%2C%20vaginal%2C%20eye%2C%20and%20dental%20symptoms.%20Results%20showed%20that%20when%20AI%20and%20physician%20recommendations%20differed%2C%20the%20AI%20suggestions%20were%20often%20rated%20as%20higher%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%2077%25%20of%20AI%20recommendations%20were%20rated%20as%20optimal%2C%20while%2067%25%20of%20physicians'%20decisions%20were%20rated%20optimal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20patients%20with%20recurring%20urinary%20tract%20infections%20sometimes%20encounter%20antibiotic%20resistance.%20Goldzweig%20said%20the%20AI%20was%20successful%20at%20identifying%20these%20patients%20and%20recommended%20a%20bacterial%20culture%20before%20prescribing%20antibiotics.%20In%20contrast%2C%20doctors%20sometimes%20prescribe%20medication%20without%20testing%2C%20which%20she%20said%20could%20result%20in%20the%20infection%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20added%20that%20the%20study%20suggests%20that%20the%20AI%20tool%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20guideline-focused%2C%20while%20physicians%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20adapt%20medical%20guidelines%20based%20on%20the%20nuance%20of%20a%20patient's%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldzweig%20said%20the%20study%20has%20limitations%2C%20though.%20It%20examined%20only%20a%20few%20medical%20conditions%20and%20didn't%20factor%20in%20the%20nuance%20of%20individual%20patient%20cases.%20Another%20limitation%20is%20that%20the%20medical%20chart%20reviewers%20could%20see%20whether%20the%20recommendation%20was%20made%20by%20the%20AI%20or%20a%20physician.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECedars-Sinai%20is%20working%20to%20expand%20CS%20Connect.%20The%20organization%20is%20piloting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-experts-say-telehealths-future-could-be-remote-monitoring-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremote%20patient%20monitoring%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20people%20manage%20chronic%20diseases%2C%20like%20high%20blood%20pressure.%20It's%20also%20planning%20to%20use%20the%20AI%20technology%20to%20connect%20in-person%20urgent%20care%20visits%20with%20virtual%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data