t%20when%20to%20schedule%20her%20first%20colonoscopy.%20Did%20she%20really%20need%20to%20do%20this%20right%20now%3F%20A%20colonoscopy%20procedure%20requires%20several%20hours%20of%20prep%20work%20at%20home%2C%20emptying%20out%20your%20colon%20with%20heavy-duty%20laxatives.%20It's%20performed%20under%20anesthesia%2C%20so%20you%20need%20someone%20to%20pick%20you%20up%20from%20the%20hospital%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20less%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20colonoscopy%20and%20more%20just%20the%20hassle%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20When%20her%20doctor%20explained%20she%20could%20order%20a%20Cologuard%20test%20and%20do%20it%20on%20her%20own%20at%20home%20with%20zero%20prep%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20no-brainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20doer%20in%20me%20is%20like%20'great%2C%20let's%20do%20it.'%20I%20want%20to%20get%20this%20done.%20Cross%20it%20off%20the%20list.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrossing%20her%20colon%20cancer%20screening%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20list%26quot%3B%20ended%20up%20taking%20a%20few%20more%20steps%2C%20though%2C%20because%20Jones's%20Cologuard%20test%20came%20back%20positive.%20Within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20Jones%20went%20in%20for%20a%20colonoscopy%2C%20which%20found%20and%20removed%20multiple%20pre-cancerous%20polyps%20in%20her%20colon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20cancer%2C%20but%20there%20were%20three%20polyps%20that%20were%20pre-cancerous%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20She%20said%20she's%20glad%20she%20was%20given%20the%20nudge%20to%20go%20under%2C%20though.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20begs%20the%20question%2C%20if%20I%20had%20waited%20a%20year%2C%20might%20that%20have%20been%20different%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECologuard%2C%20made%20by%20Exact%20Sciences%2C%20was%20first%20approved%20in%202014.%20In%20late%202024%2C%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20approved%20Cologuard%20Plus%2C%20which%20is%20more%20accurate%20than%20the%20regular%20Cologuard%20test%20and%20detects%20around%2095%25%20of%20