C%20called%20Shield%2C%20was%20FDA-approved%20in%20July%202024.%20It's%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20suite%20of%20%26quot%3Bliquid%20biopsies%26quot%3B%20that%20use%20blood%20to%20help%20doctors%20gain%20insights%20about%20cancer%2C%20whether%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-environmental-causes-microplastics-antibiotics-sleep-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20diagnosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20in%20later%20stages%20to%20inform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscientists-test-low-carb-for-breast-cancer-treatment-chemotherapy-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20treatment%20decisions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuardant%20CEO%20Helmy%20Eltoukhy%20told%20BI%20he%20hopes%20that%20Shield%20can%20soon%20be%20harnessed%20to%20identify%20even%20more%20cancers%2C%20including%20some%20that%20are%20notoriously%20hard%20to%20detect%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-heart-palpitations-stage-4-pancreatic-cancer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epancreatic%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20federally%20funded%20study%20is%20recruiting%2024%2C000%20people%20across%20the%20US%20to%20test%20out%20Shield%20on%20multiple%20cancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20beauty%20of%20this%20test%3A%20think%20of%20it%20as%20your%20iPhone%2C%20where%20initially%20it%20only%20had%20a%20few%20features.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20has%20a%20thousand%20features%2C%26quot%3B%20Eltoukhy%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatricia%20James%2C%20now%2077%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20patients%20to%20try%20Shield%20in%20Guardant's%20pivotal%20clinical%20trial%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20its%20FDA%20approval%20last%20year.%20As%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffired-with-cancer-reporter-baking-influencer-dream-job-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20survivor%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw