0getting%20it%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forgan-age-test-what-proteomics-can-reveal-about-health-longevity-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escreening%20tests%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentioned%20here%2C%20Shield%20does%20have%20a%20risk%20of%20false-positive%20and%20false-negative%20results%2C%20but%20those%20inaccuracies%20decrease%20as%20cancer%20progresses.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20further%20along%20cancer%20is%2C%20the%20better%20the%20test%20is%20at%20detecting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMethod%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBlood%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnce%20every%20three%20years%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECost%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGenerally%20covered%20by%20insurance%20for%20those%20over%2045%2C%20and%20by%20Medicare%20for%20older%20adults.%20The%20test%20costs%20around%20%241%2C500%20out-of-pocket.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20poop%20involved%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERequires%20a%20doctor's%20visit%20to%20collect%20blood.%20Also%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eroughly%201%20of%20every%2010%20patients%20who%20don't%20have%20colon%20cancer%20may%20receive%20a%20false%20positive%20result%2C%20and%201%20in%206%20who%20do%20have%20cancer%20may%20receive%20a%20false%20negative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0e02909-b4c7-470c-aadb-d761ab65ee92%5C%22%3EThe%20breath%20test%20for%20colon%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20that%20instead%20of%20collecting%20blood%20or%20poop%20to%20screen%20for%20colon%20cancer%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20breathe%20out%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20companies%2C%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Israel%20are%20working%20on%20innovative%20cancer%20screening%20tests%20that%20would%20pick%20up%20on%20volatile%20organic%20compounds%20in%20your%20breath.%20It's%20essentially%20like%