ity%20that%20energizes%20me%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELenz%20said%20his%20students%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20work%20in%20large%20technology%20companies%2C%20banks%2C%20entrepreneurial%20start-ups%2C%20and%20investment%20and%20brokerage%20firms.%20Glassdoor's%20salary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glassdoor.com%2FSalary%2FFintech-Software-Engineer-Salaries-E816003_D_KO8%2C25.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20fintech%20engineers%20ranges%20from%20%24109%2C000%20to%20%24170%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20but%20Lenz%20said%20that%20based%20on%20conversations%20with%20his%20former%20students%2C%20the%20range%20can%20sometimes%20stretch%20to%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235813778-1495-4b6f-bdfc-c59a46571ec3%5C%22%3ECuriosity%20is%20key%20to%20a%20fintech%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKathleen%20DeRose%2C%20the%20academic%20director%20of%20the%20Master%20of%20Science%20in%20Fintech%20program%20at%20New%20York%20University%2C%20said%20new%20advancements%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%20keep%20fintech%20evolving%20and%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20prospects%20for%20fintech%20engineers%20%26quot%3Breflect%20the%20tech%20transformations%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20surge%20of%20multibillion-dollar%20companies%20in%20the%20fintech%20space%20also%20%26quot%3Bsuggests%20the%20prospects%20are%20really%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DeRose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20DeRose%20speaks%20with%20hiring%20managers%20and%20recruiters%2C%20she's%20increasingly%20hearing%20a%20desired%20characteristic%20that%20goes%20beyond%20technical%20skills%3A%20curiosity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20the%20technical%20chops%2C%20but%20the%20ability%20to%20learn%20quickly%20and%20have%20the%20curiosity%20to%20do%20so%20is%20the%20adaptive%20power%20that's%20wanted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20recommended%20choosing%20to%20work%20with%20companies%20%26quot%3Bthat%20g