e%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-scared-bearish-sp500-price-targets-stock-market-crash-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elowest%20price%20targets%20among%20strategists%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20major%20Wall%20Street%20institutions.%20His%20caution%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20warranted%2C%20as%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20plunged%2019%25%20from%20mid-February%20to%20mid-April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBannister%20has%20a%20couple%20of%20arguments%20in%20support%20of%20his%20outlook%3A%20valuations%20are%20high%2C%20and%20economic%20growth%20is%20likely%20to%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20look%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20economy.%20How%20is%20the%20consumer%20and%20capital%20spending%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannister%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20core%20GDP%2C%20or%20real%20final%20consumer%20sales%20and%20fixed%20business%20investment.%20Standard%20GDP%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20volatile%20inventory%20building%20that%20firms%20did%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%20to%20prepare%20for%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20looks%20to%20us%20like%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20slowdown%20in%20the%20second%20half%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20this%20month%2C%20Bannister%20shared%20the%20chart%20below%2C%20showing%20the%20relationship%20between%20core%20GDP%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20returns.%20Current%20trends%20imply%20that%20year-over-year%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20returns%20are%20set%20to%20dip%20negative%20in%20the%20months%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221874%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp%20500%20vs%20core%20gdp%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fe07885e81483682e7899%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStifel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20valuations%2C%20Bannister%20said%20stocks%20ar