C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emove%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20even%20though%20the%20community%20college%20and%20then%20university%20I%20chose%20to%20attend%20were%20within%20forty-minutes%20of%20my%20family%20home.%20I%20desperately%20wanted%20the%20independence%20living%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-declutterer-how-to-dorm-room-organized-mess-free-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edorm%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20have%20allowed%20me.%20Yet%2C%20even%20though%20I%20worked%20three%20jobs%20while%20attending%20school%20full-time%2C%20there%20was%20simply%20no%20way%20to%20make%20rent%2C%20or%20dorm%20fees%2C%20within%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20graduated%20college%20and%20moved%20on%20to%20graduate%20school%2C%20I%20began%20teaching%20my%20first%20college-level%20classes.%20What%20my%20students%20shared%20with%20me%20was%20eye-opening.%20Dorm%20life%20isn't%20nearly%20as%20fun%20and%20exciting%20as%20they%20make%20it%20seem%20in%20the%20movies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20my%20students%20confessed%20all%20of%20their%20roommate%20issues%2C%20the%20happier%20I%20became%20with%20my%20own%20decision%20to%20skip%20out%20on%20the%20dorm%20or%20off-campus%20apartment%20experience.%20Here's%20why%2C%2025%20years%20later%2C%20I%20no%20longer%20regret%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-student-lived-at-home-saved-thousands-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enot%20living%20in%20a%20dorm%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229792c8d4-0ce9-4255-9351-dc21274f98a6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoommates%20can%20be%20a%20nightmare%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20I%20had%20several%20students%20come%20to%20my%20class%20frustrated%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prevent-deal-with-burnout-college-students-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexhausted%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Because%20I%20teach%20writing