0Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20home%20was%20not%20just%20about%20survival.%20It%20was%20about%20nurturing%20a%20dream.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20may%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20for%20a%20middle-class%20person%20to%20do%20such%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20Debashish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%20believe%20anything%20is%20possible%20if%20one%20has%20belief%2C%20grit%2C%20and%20passion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20lockdown%20in%202020%20that%20Debraj%20first%20picked%20up%20the%20guitar.%20With%20no%20formal%20background%20in%20music%20production%2C%20he%20began%20learning%20the%20instrument%20through%20online%20tutorials%20and%20by%20ear.%20It%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20long%20for%20him%20to%20realise%20that%20music%20was%20not%20just%20an%20outlet%2C%20but%20his%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20Debraj%20took%20his%20music%20to%20the%20street%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20busk%20came%20after%20watching%20several%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446677%2Fkaushalya-chaudhary-sidhi-marwari-rajasthan-clean-food-brand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20street%20performers%20around%20the%20world.%20Debraj%20was%20fascinated%20by%20the%20idea%20that%20anyone%20could%20create%20a%20space%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20bustling%20city%20%E2%80%94%20without%20a%20stage%2C%20spotlight%2C%20or%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20dad%20also%20suggested%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20thought%20it%20would%20help%20me%20express%20myself%20and%20show%20the%20public%20my%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cpre%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-code%5C%22%3E%3Ccode%3E%26lt%3Biframe%20src%3D%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D476%26amp%3Bhref%3Dhttps%253A