a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-1536x1023.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-1200x800.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107-150x100.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-6_11zon-1753267107.jpeg%201600w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475018%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushmita%E2%80%99s%20sessions%20combine%20science%20with%20hands-on%20learning%20to%20rethink%20invasive%20species%20as%20resources.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20the%20cycle%20repeats%20%E2%80%94%20draining%20public%20funds%20while%20offering%20no%20lasting%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20breakthrough%20in%20Germany%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20Sushmita%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20a%20better%20solution%20led%20her%20far%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20labs%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Hamburg%20in%20Germany.%20She%20had%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20prestigious%20International%20Sustainability%20Academy%20(ISA)%20fellowship%2C%20which%20supports%20young%20changemakers%20tackling%20global%20environmental%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20hundreds%20of%20applicants%2C%20she%20was%20one%20of%20only%2012%20fellows%20chosen%20worldwide%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20only%20one%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sushmita%E2%80%99s%20workshops%20teach%20how%201%20kg%20of%20water%20hyacinth%20can%20be%20turned%20into%2030%20sheets%20of%20paper.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan_11zon-1753267363-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475020%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushmita%E2%80%99s%20workshops%20teach%20how%201%20kg%20of%20water%20hyacinth%20can%20be%20turned%20into%2030%20sheets%20of%20paper.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20University%20of%20Hamburg%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20a%20wood%20chemistry%20lab%20with%20Professor%20Bodosake%2C%20who%20specialises%20in%20pulp-making%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20began%20experimenting%20with%20water%20hyacinth%20as%20a%20paper%20raw%20material.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20surprised%20even%20the%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20making%20paper%20from%20wood%20pulp%20uses%20around%2060%25%20soda.%20But%20we%20found%20that%20with%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20you%20only%20need%20about%206%25.%20And%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20pulp%20was%20excellent%20%E2%80%94%20strong%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20work%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20breakthrough%20proved%20what%20she%20had%20long%20suspected%20%E2%80%94%20water%20hyacinth%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20a%20burden.%20With%20the%20right%20technique%2C%20it%20could%20become%20a%20sustainable%2C%20scalable%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBack%20home%2C%20but%20not%20yet%20on%20board%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnergised%20by%20her%20success%20in%20Germany%2C%20Sushmita%20returned%20to%20India%20with%20a%20clear%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20to%20scale%20up%20the%20process%20and%20introduce%20water%20hyacinth%20paper%20into%20mainstream%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20paper%20industries%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20be%20a%20new%20income%20source%20for%20communities%20that%20pulp%20water%20hyacinth%20and%20supply%20it%20to%20factories.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20quickly%20ran%20into%20a%20familiar%20roadblock%3A%20hesitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20data%20and%20lab%20results%2C%20paper%20manufacturers%20were%20reluctant%20to%20test%20alternative%20raw%20materials.%20Adopting%20a%20new%20process%20meant%20investment%2C%20trial%20runs%2C%20and%20regulatory%20approvals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20take%20the%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-226x300.jpeg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-768x1021.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-1156x1536.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-150x199.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613-1200x1595.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-9_11zon-1753267613.jpeg%201204w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20with%20proper%20patents%20and%20publications%2C%20the%20industry%20would%20take%20at%20least%20three%20years%20to%20switch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20three%20years%2C%20a%20lot%20can%20happen%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20realisation%20shifted%20her%20focus.%20If%20industries%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20move%2C%20she%20would%20start%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20method%20to%20the%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushmita%20knew%20the%20method%20would%20only%20matter%20if%20people%20could%20use%20it.%20So%20she%20began%20conducting%20hands-on%20workshops%2C%20sharing%20her%20process%20with%20students%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20women%20from%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20started%20training%20people%20to%20make%20paper%20from%20water%20hyacinth.%20Many%20colleges%20are%20interested%20in%20adapting%20it%20for%20their%20own%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20National%20College%2C%20Trichy%2C%20she%20ran%20a%20two-day%20workshop%20that%20combined%20science%20with%20skill-building.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20theory%20session%20on%20the%20first%20day%20about%20water%20hyacinths%2C%20but%20the%20second%20day%20we%20had%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20creating%20the%20papers%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ishika%2C%20a%20student%20who%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-226x300.jpeg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-768x1020.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-1156x1536.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-150x199.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-1200x1594.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842.jpeg%201459w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475034%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20those%20students%20are%20using%20their%20own%20handmade%20paper%20for%20greeting%20cards%20and%20college%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20campuses%2C%20she%20has%20also%20trained%20over%20150%20women%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20group%20of%20middle-aged%20women%20in%20Velachery%2C%20Chennai%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Environment.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20two%20workshops%20for%20the%20Ministry%2C%20three%20for%20colleges%2C%20and%20a%20few%20more%20are%20lined%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sushmita%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20not%20just%20awareness%2C%20but%20adoption.%20The%20more%20people%20who%20learned%20the%20method%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20it%20was%20to%20catch%20on%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20places%20overrun%20by%20hyacinth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20pond%20to%20page%3A%20The%20paper-making%20process%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20turning%20water%20hyacinth%20into%20paper%20is%20surprisingly%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20and%20designed%20to%20be%20both%20cost-effective%20and%20environmentally%20conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20begins%20with%20harvesting%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20stems%2C%20which%20are%20then%20sun-dried%20and%20boiled%20in%20an%20alkaline%20solution%20to%20break%20down%20the%20fibres.%20This%20softened%20pulp%20is%20beaten%20and%20mixed%20with%20water%20and%20a%20natural%20plant-based%20binder%20to%20create%20a%20slurry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mixture%20is%20poured%20onto%20mesh%20frames%2C%20where%20the%20water%20drains%20out%20and%20the%20thin%20layer%20of%20pulp%20is%20left%20to%20dry%20under%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__content%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20other%20small-scale%20paper%20makers%2C%20Sushmita%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20newspaper%20pulp%20to%20hold%20the%20paper%20together.%20Nor%20does%20she%20bleach%20it%20to%20make%20it%20look%20%E2%80%9Ccleaner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20use%20only%20natural%20binders%2C%20and%20the%20paper%20retains%20its%20natural%20greenish%20tint.%20I%20believe%20the%20quality%20of%20paper%20is%20defined%20by%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20write%20on%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20how%20white%20it%20looks%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20process%20is%20quick%20and%20low-cost.%20%E2%80%9CWith%201%20kg%20of%20wet%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20you%20can%20make%2030%20A4%20sheets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20estimates.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20harvesting%20to%20making%20the%20pulp%2C%20it%20takes%20about%2025%20minutes.%20The%20drying%20takes%20another%2045.%20With%20practice%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it%20even%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20in%2015%20minutes.%20And%20the%20cost%20per%20sheet%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%202.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-226x300.jpeg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-768x1020.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-1156x1536.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-150x199.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911-1200x1594.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-12_11zon-1753267911.jpeg%201459w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-475039%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainable%20change%20happens%20from%20the%20bottom%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20workshops%20have%20sparked%20interest%20and%20early%20adoption%2C%20Sushmita%20is%20clear-eyed%20about%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20by%20making%20handmade%20paper%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20restore%20an%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWater%20hyacinth%20grows%20at%20such%20a%20rapid%20pace%20%E2%80%94%20one%20hectare%20can%20produce%20up%20to%20700%20tonnes%20of%20it%20in%20a%20year.%20That%E2%80%99s%20something%20only%20large%20industries%20can%20tackle%20effectively.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20she%20believes%20community-led%20solutions%20like%20hers%20can%20nudge%20the%20system%20forward.%20By%20building%20awareness%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20potential%2C%20and%20training%20people%20directly%20affected%20by%20the%20plant%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20create%20enough%20momentum%20for%20wider%20institutional%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-11_11zon-1753267985-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-11_11zon-1753267985-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-11_11zon-1753267985-226x300.jpeg%20226w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-11_11zon-1753267985-768x1020.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%